sine_stimulus Installation instructions 
=========================================

Requirements: 
-------------

- Python v2.5
  http://www.python.org/

- pylibusb v0.1
  
Installation:
-------------

The package uses the Python setuptools, you can build it by calling

  python setup.py install

A sample udev rules file is given in the sine_stimulus/udev_rules directory.

which installs the package on your system. 
See the "Installing Python Modules" manual inside your Python documentation 
or at http://docs.python.org/inst/inst.html if you want to customize the
build process or the target location.